<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.5">
<l>cempoṉ nīḷmuṭi yeṅkaḷi ravaṇaṉ cītai yeṉpatōr teyvamko ṇarntu</l>
<l>vampu lāmkaṭi kāvilci ṟaiyā vaitta tēkuṟṟa  māyiṟṟuk  kāṇīr</l>
<l>kumpa ṉōṭuni kumpaṉum paṭṭāṉ kūṟṟam maṉiṭa māyvantu tōṉṟi</l>
<l>yampi ṉālemmaik koṉṟiṭu kiṉṟa tañci ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Rāvaṇa with a high crown of rose gold, having carried away</l>
<l rend="indent">a deity named Sītā,</l>
<l>Keeping her as a captive, in a guarded garden where scents wafted,</l>
<l rend="indent">was wrong! Look!</l>
<l>Kumbha and Nikumbha perished. Death, coming and appearing</l>
<l rend="indent">in the form of a man,</l>
<l>Is utterly destroying us with arrows. We are frightened.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
